00:25:14.670 --> 00:25:17.400
But we can do one more thing.

00:25:17.400 --> 00:25:20.540
These are reading scores this
way, this is the measure of

00:25:20.540 --> 00:25:22.110
the white matter organization
from the

00:25:22.110 --> 00:25:23.970
Diffusion Tensor Imaging.

00:25:23.970 --> 00:25:26.630
Each of these as an individual
person now.

00:25:26.630 --> 00:25:29.380
So the open dots are the people
who had typical reading

00:25:29.380 --> 00:25:30.940
development.

00:25:30.940 --> 00:25:34.550
The filled dots are the people
