00:26:09.960 --> 00:26:12.210
a lot, and you were exercising
this part of the brain, and

00:26:12.210 --> 00:26:15.240
altered its physical
structure.

00:26:15.240 --> 00:26:17.200
And the answer is
we don't know.

00:26:17.200 --> 00:26:20.080
How could we know?

00:26:20.080 --> 00:26:21.330
How could we know?

00:26:23.350 --> 00:26:26.400
If you were scientists and were
